processes.- In: Thermoactivated spectroscopy of defects in ionic
crystals,
Riga, Latv.State Univ. Press, 1983, p.23-38 (in Russian).
</p>
<p> <B><I><FONT COLOR="FF3300">1984</FONT></I></B> </p>
<p><a name="B6"></a>6. Kantorovich L.N. Multipole theory of the
polarization
of solids by point defect. II.The point charge approximation. -
