1985, Riga, Latv. State Univ.Press, p.146- 166 (in Russian).
</p>
<p> <B><I><FONT COLOR="FF3300">1986</FONT></I></B> </p>
<p><a name="B11"></a>11. Kantorovich L.N. Multipole theory of the
polarization
of solids by point defect. III.Transition energy calculations, the
