of non - point charges. - Phys.stat.sol.(b), v.137, 1986, p.229-240.
</p>
<p><a name="B12"></a>12. Shluger A.L., Kotomin E.A. and Kantorovich
L.N.
Quantum-chemical simulation of impurity-induced trapping of a hole: [Li]<sup>0</sup>
centre in MgO. - J.Phys.C:Solid State Phys., v.19, 1986, p.4183-4199.
